snippet.title: Super Sami Roll - Launch Trailer | PS5
snippet.description: Super Sami Roll tumbles its way to PlayStation 5 this Fall! Join Sami on an exciting adventure, filled with high-speed traversal, tricky platforming and tongue-grappling action, just like the good old days of gaming!
